Example: 'Find all uses of student_id across the backend.'
8. Frontend Support
- Build new React components or pages
- Style using Tailwind CSS
- Write React testing logic
Example: 'Create a ResultPage to show quiz score and certificate link.'
9. Interactive Workflows
- Create branches, open PRs, suggest diffs
- Auto-commit file updates based on instructions
Example: 'Create a new branch called feedback-service and add new models.'
10. Learning & Mentorship
- Ask Codex to explain unfamiliar syntax or logic
- Request architecture or design best practices
Example: 'What is the best way to structure a FastAPI microservice repo?'